    IBoxResponseParser

    public class ErrorResponseParser
extends DefaultBoxJSONResponseParser
    Parser to parse DefaultBoxResponse into BoxServerError objects. It analyse the response JSON String and uses Jackson JSON processor to generate BoxServerError objects.
